      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-3-d" mid="80" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>Hmm... This is not as easy as I thought.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Terramai strokes his chin)</FONT><BR>It must be in somewhere in Lotus Marsh....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Teramai.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-3-e" mid="82" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="81"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Maybe the natives of Lotus Marsh might know something.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Teramai.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-3-!next" mid="83" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>That's right. The natives might know something.<BR>Since Sidel said that he knows some natives well, I think it'd be better to ask for Sidel's help in getting some information tentang the Mirror of Truth.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Teramai.dds" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Teramai.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-3-" mid="85" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="56"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>Hmm...it's not as easy as I thought it would be.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Terramai strokes his chin)</FONT><BR>We should get more information. I will call you soon. Until then, concentrate on training.<BR>
